the us technology consists of a special way of irradiating 
flies to make them sterile under the strategy tens of millions of 
flies would be sterilized at a specially outfitted usmexican 
laboratory in mexico and released in libya matings would 
eventually cause the insect to die out 
the united states became the unquestioned expert on screwworm 
flies after years of devastating infestation in the us southwest 
