essential when the fullscale fly release scheduled to last up to 
two years is under way 
the us government has cooperated in other ways larval samples 
have been analyzed in a north dakota facility and ms bonkowsky 
said a libyan was granted a visa to work with us experts there 
there are also problems between the fao and the united states 
