voice votes and sent it to the full foreign affairs committee 
failure to implement the formula by the five permanent security 
council members to strengthen the un presence in cambodia could 
produce results almost too awful to contemplate return of the 
khmer rouge blamed for more than a million cambodian deaths 
during their 197578 rule over the southeast asian country solarz 
