<TEXT>
west german leaders on wednesday praised 
president mikhail s gorbachevs apparent acceptance of 
reunification as a signal that may instill hope in east germans 
fearful of the uncertainties of reform 
chancellor helmut kohl called the kremlin chiefs latest 
comments on german unity encouraging and foreign minister 
