article a suggestion that gorbachev divide his posts retaining the 
presidency and surrendering the party leadership he said in an 
interview he believes this issue will come to the fore soon and 
that as president he would have much more trust than as head of 
the party of this party 
drozdov declined to say who changed it but other sources said 
the decision was made inside the newspaper not from higher up 
as printed the editorial said simply in the end he is our 
president and more than anything he is our president 
in pravdas report on a discussion by four scholars historian 
yevgeny ambartsumov said gorbachev appeared unable to take decisive 
action because of the threat to his position ambartsumov said the 
countrys president has few legal guarantees of his position even 
though the congress of peoples deputies elected gorbachev last may 
