late sen henry jackson dwash in 1974 coauthoried the 
jacksonvanik amendment barriers imposing high tariffs on imports 
from the soviet union and its allies and denying them export 
credits to buy us goods 
vanik said repealing the law entirely as us business leaders 
have urged is unlikely because 20 percent of the public and 
