national association of truck stop operators at its annual 
convention in las vegas on thursday 
he said he believes that alcohol and drug abuse is a relatively 
small problem in the trucking industry far less than for drivers 
as a whole but he said there was room for improvement and that the 
industry should show no tolerance for those who break the rules 
