hospitals broadcast appeals over all christian radio stations 
for urgent blood donations to cope with what one nurse at the hotel 
dieu french missionary hospital the biggest in east beirut called 
a deluge of casualties 
the morgue is packed and dozens of wounded are bleeding on 
stretchers in corridors said the nurse who asked not to be 
identified 
stray shells exploded around the ports of beirut and jounieh 
forcing 18 ships to steam for open sea police said 
one of the injured was news photographer george samarejian of 
the independent annahar daily police said samarejian 45 was 
