men were fighting for our survival 
we shall respond to each shell with 10 shells he said in a 
statement broadcast by christian radio stations we shall not 
allow those blinded by the lust for power to slaughter the lebanese 
forces 
both sides ignored ceasefire appeals from the vatican and 
lebanons maronite catholic patriarch nasrallah sfeir 
