plans for a palestinianisraeli dialogue to break the stalemated 
middle east peacemaking process 
also on the agenda is the outcry from the plo and arab states 
against resettlement of soviet and eastern european jews in the 
israeliheld west bank and gaza strip 
the arab league peace plan was endorsed by the lebanese 
parliament members at a threeweek conference in the saudi mountain 
resort of taif in october 
