<TEXT>
he considers himself a loyal member of the 
communist party and remains an admirer of senior chinese leader 
deng xiaoping but in the waning days of last springs 
prodemocracy demonstrations gao xin and three others staged a 
hunger strike in tiananmen square for that he spent six months in 
