indefinitely in midmarch the other layoffs stem from production 
reductions at other plants 
ford motor co has avoided indefinite layoffs by eliminating 
overtime and temporarily shutting down a variety of its factories 
closing or cutting production at big three assembly plants 
typically mean layoffs at component and supplier plants operated by 
the automakers or other companies its difficult to estimate how 
many layoffs may occur because of the assembly plant closings but 
automakers have said it could be thousands of jobs 
