the registration filing revealed several situations at the parent 
company 
fords dec 15 1989 sale of all the outstanding stock of 
rouge steel company to marico acquisition corp was below book 
value the amount of the charge to net income has not yet been 
determined but could range up to 500 million for the fourth 
quarter and full year 1989 
