indemnify rouge steel for environmental matters prior to the 
sale ford is unable at this time to determine the amount of its 
potential responsibility for such environmental matters however 
such costs could be substantial 
on jan 12 ford announced plans to sell ford aerospace but 
it is uncertain when or at what price such sale may occur 
the acquisition of associates a major consumer loan concern 
and jaguar plc the british luxury carmaker have used and will 
continue to use substantial amounts of available cash 
consequently it is anticipated that ford and its affilates will 
substantially increase borrowings in 1990 
