attendants and other employees will be redesigned malek said 
northwest leads the industry in transpacific flights which can 
be 13 to 14 hours long malek said thats a long trip you want 
a tranquil comfortable pleasing decor package 
flight attendants will be added on some flights he said and 
the airline will spend 30 million over the five years to clean 
planes more often he didnt elaborate on how the airline will 
allocate the remaining 110 million 
malek held a news conference in detroit northwests largest 
hub after briefing an annual conference of the airlines sales and 
