atampt credit corp said wednesday it 
purchased two financing divisions of pacificorp credit inc a 
subsidiary of pacificorp financial services for 460 million 
the distribution financing division helps support equipment 
sales for manufacturers by providing financing for their customers 
said pacificorp spokesman mike nelson 
the asset leasing and financing division with field offices in 
atlanta and denver helps provide financing for franchises such as 
restaurant chains and media customers nelson said 
the two divisions based in portland ore were purchased for 
cash obtained mostly through the sale of debt by atampt credit corp 
and preferred stock issued by atampt commercial finance corp to 
pacificorp credit 
atampt credit corp is a wholly owned subsidiary of american 
telegraph and telephone co that does a wide variety of equipment 
leasing and financing 
